### Hadith 2:243

*Narrated Abu Huraira*

Allah's Apostle said, "Satan puts three knots at the back of the head of
any of you if he is asleep. On every knot he reads and exhales the
following words, 'The night is long, so stay asleep.' When one wakes up
and remembers Allah, one knot is undone; and when one performs ablution,
the second knot is undone, and when one prays the third knot is undone
and one gets up energetic with a good heart in the morning; otherwise
one gets up lazy and with a mischievous heart."

